/05/style/hector-xtravaganza-memorial.html|title=The Extravagant Life of Hector Xtravaganza|first=Jacob|last=Bernstein|date=January 5, 2019|newspaper=The New York Times}}</ref>\n* [[Venus Xtravaganza]] \u2013 late transgender performer and voguer (House of Xtravaganza)<ref name=\"medvenus\">{{cite web |url=https://medium.com/th-ink/justice-for-venus-xtravaganza-1cbd45bc504a |title=Justice for Venus Xtravaganza |last=Iovannone |first=Jeffry J. |date=July 12, 2018 |website= [[Medium (website)|Medium]] |publisher=A Medium Corporation |access-date=May 31, 2019 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190531231428/https://medium.com/th-ink/justice-for-venus-xtravaganza-1cbd45bc504a |archive-date=May 31, 2019 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n====Drag====\n* [[Acid Betty]] \u2013 drag queen (contestant on the [[RuPaul's Drag Race (season 8)|eighth season]] of ''[[RuPaul's Drag Race]]'')<ref name=\"hpab\">{{Cite news |url=https://www.huffpost.com/entry/acid-betty-after-dark_n_5512496 |title=After Dark: Meet NYC's Acid Betty, Artist And Nightlife Personality |last=Nichols |first=James Michael |date=June 22, 2014 |website=HuffPost |publisher=Janet Balis |access-date=November 12, 2019 |archive-date=November 12, 2019 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191112075542/https://www.huffpost.com/entry/acid-betty-after-dark_n_5512496 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n* [[Aja (entertainer)|Aja]] \u2013 [[drag queen]] and [[rapper]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.them.us/story/aja-rapper-name-change-interview|title=Exclusive: Nonbinary Rapper Aja Discusses Their Name Change|first=Cond\u00e9|last=Nast|website=them.}}</ref>\n* [[Aquaria (drag queen)|Aquaria]] \u2013 drag queen and performance artist (winner of the [[RuPaul's Drag Race (season 10)|tenth season]] of ''RuPaul's Drag Race'')<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://nypost.com/2018/06/01/rupauls-drag-race-queens-share-their-beauty-secrets/|title='RuPaul's Drag Race' queens share their beauty secrets|first=Eric|last=Hegedus|date=June 2, 2018}}</