ian Hutchison 2017.jpg|[[Brian Hutchison]]\nFile:Juliana Huxtable.jpg|[[Juliana Huxtable]]\nFile:CheyenneJacksonKSimone.jpg|[[Cheyenne Jackson]]\nFile:Marc Jacobs SXSW 2017 (cropped).jpg|[[Marc Jacobs]]\nFile:Corey Johnson 2015.jpg|[[Corey Johnson (politician)|Corey Johnson]]\nFile:Bill T. Jones.jpg|[[Bill T. Jones]]\nFile:DJ Keoki.JPG|[[DJ Keoki]]\nFile:Bradshaw performing in 2017.jpg|[[Cakes da Killa]]\nFile:Calvin Klein 2011 Shankbone.JPG|[[Calvin Klein]]\nFile:Sally Kohn by Gage Skidmore.jpg|[[Sally Kohn]]\nFile:Michael Kors, Photographed by Ed Kavishe for Fashion Wire Press.jpg|[[Michael Kors]]\nFile:Eva_Kotchever_(\u201cEve_Addams\u201d)_on_right_with_an_unidentified_woman.jpg|[[Eva Kotchever]] (on right)\nFile:Larry Kramer 2010 Photo - David Shankbone.jpg|[[Larry Kramer]]\nFile:KIll Your Darlings- John Krokidas (9765358411) (cropped).jpg|[[John Krokidas]]\nFile:Tony Kushner - Hollywood and Socialism - The Laura Flanders Show 2.png|[[Tony Kushner]]\nFile:Photo of M. Lamar by M. Lamar.jpg|[[M Lamar]]\nFile:Matteo Lane 2014.png|[[Matteo Lane]]\nFile:NathanLane2018.jpg|[[Nathan Lane]]\nFile:Le1f by Gergely Csatari 1.jpg|[[Le1f]]\nFile:Annie Leibovitz-SF-1-Crop.jpg|[[Annie Leibovitz]]\nFile:Redlight Traffics Inaugural Dignity Gala (10358998094) (cropped).jpg|[[Don Lemon]]\nFile:Life Ball 2014 red carpet 075 Amanda Lepore.jpg|[[Amanda Lepore]]\nFile:HeddaLettuce.jpg|[[Hedda Lettuce]]\nFile:Phillip Lim, Copyright Ed Kavishe.JPG|[[Phillip Lim]]\nFile:Paul Lisicky.jpg|[[Paul Lisicky]]\nFile:Jennie Livingston.jpg|[[Jennie Livingston]]\nFile:Bryan Llenas at Bravo Awards.jpg|[[Bryan Llenas]]\nFile:Michael Lucas 2011.jpg|[[Michael Lucas (director)|Michael Lucas]]\nFile:Dragcon-4 (47937164822).jpg|[[Manila Luzon]]\nFile:Rachel Maddow in Seattle cropped.png|[[Rachel Maddow]]\nFile:02 Leiomy Mizrahi by EbruYildiz 02.jpg|[[Leiomy Maldonado]]\nFile:Chella_Man,_January_2019.png|[[Chella Man]]\nFile:Jaime-Manrique-683x1024.jpg|[[Jaime Manrique]]\nFile:Director Joe Mantello.jpg|[