ws/people/profiles/sandra-bernhard-bisexuality-and-savage-wit-397472.html|title=Sandra Bernhard: Bisexuality and savage wit|date=October 22, 2007|website=The Independent}}</ref>\n* [[Matt Bomer]] \u2013 actor and director<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.out.com/matt-bomer|title=Matt Bomer \u2013 openly gay American actor and father|website=out.com}}</ref>\n* [[Candis Cayne]] \u2013 transgender actress<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2004/11/06/nyregion/keep-your-eye-on-the-road-if-you-can.html|title=Keep Your Eye on the Road (If You Can)|first=Erik|last=Piepenburg|date=November 6, 2004|work=The New York Times}}</ref>\n* [[Bill Condon]] \u2013 director, screenwriter, and producer<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.passportmagazine.com/departments/BillCondon.php|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120405210339/http://www.passportmagazine.com/departments/BillCondon.php|url-status=dead|archive-date=April 5, 2012|title=Bill Condon \u2013 Gay and Lesbian Travel|date=April 5, 2012}}</ref>\n* [[Laverne Cox]] \u2013 transgender actress<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://time.com/2973497/laverne-cox-emmy/|title=Laverne Cox Is the First Transgender Person Nominated for an Emmy|website=Time}}</ref>\n* [[Lee Daniels]] \u2013 director, screenwriter, and producer<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.out.com/out-exclusives/out100-2013/2013/11/13/out100-lee-daniels|title=Out100: Lee Daniels|date=November 13, 2013|website=out.com}}</ref>\n* [[Billy Eichner]] \u2013 actor, comedian, and writer<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.heyalma.com/18-things-to-know-about-billy-eichner/|title=18 Things to Know About Billy Eichner|date=July 26, 2019|website=Alma}}</ref>\n* [[Fredrik Eklund]] \u2013 real estate broker, co-star of ''[[Million Dollar Listing New York]]''<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.bravotv.com/the-daily-dish/fredrik-eklund-failed-pregnancy-surrogate-loses-babies|title=Fredrik Eklund Shares Devastating News: \"We've Had a Failed Pregnancy\"|date=September 15, 2015|website=Bravo TV Offic