culture/drag-race-season-10-manila-luzon-narcbar-interview |access-date= November 23, 2019 |title=Manila still calls New York home|website=standardhotels.com}}</ref><ref name=\"manila\">{{cite news |url=https://socialitelife.com/manila-luzon-socialite-life-interview/ |title=Manila Luzon \u2013 The Socialite Life Interview |last=Fitzgerald |first=Christine |date=December 14, 2018 |access-date=November 12, 2019 |website=socialitelife.com |publisher=Socialite Life |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191112082727/https://socialitelife.com/manila-luzon-socialite-life-interview/ |archive-date=November 12, 2019 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n* [[Alexis Michelle]] \u2013 singer and drag queen (contestant on the [[RuPaul's Drag Race (season 9)|ninth season]] of ''RuPaul's Drag Race'')<ref name=\"amout\">{{cite magazine |url=https://www.out.com/michael-musto/2017/3/20/drag-race-season-9-star-alexis-michelle-drag-activism-boyfriends |title=''Drag Race'' Season 9 Star Alexis Michelle on Drag, Activism & Boyfriends |date=March 20, 2017 |last=Musto |first=Michael |author-link=Michael Musto |magazine=[[Out (magazine)|Out]] |publisher=Joe Landry |archive-date=June 28, 2018 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180628045715/https://www.out.com/michael-musto/2017/3/20/drag-race-season-9-star-alexis-michelle-drag-activism-boyfriends |url-status=live |access-date=November 12, 2019 }}</ref>\n* [[Milk (drag queen)|Milk]] \u2013 drag performer and fashion model<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.out.com/out-exclusives/love-issue/2015/01/12/out-love-ballet-dancer-james-whiteside-aka-jbdubs-performer-dan|title=Out Love: Ballet dancer James Whiteside (aka JbDubs) & performer Dan Donigan (aka Milk)|date=January 12, 2015|website=out.com}}</ref>\n* [[Pearl (drag queen)|Pearl]] \u2013 drag queen (contestant on the seventh season of ''RuPaul's Drag Race'')<ref name=\"pearlny\">{{cite news |url=https://www.huffpost.com/entry/rupauls-drag-race-season-seven-cast_n_6276782 |title='RuPaul's Drag Rac