| Left office\n! scope=col | Tenure\n! scope=col | Cabinet\n|-\n| align=center | [[File:Karl Eirik Schj\u00f8tt-Pedersen.jpg|100x100px]]\n! scope=row | [[Karl Eirik Schj\u00f8tt-Pedersen]]\n| style=\"background:#FFB6B6\" | [[Labour Party (Norway)|Labour]] || {{dts|format=dmy|2000|03|17}} || {{dts|format=dmy|2001|10|19}} || {{ayd|2000|03|17|2001|10|19}} || [[First cabinet Stoltenberg|Stoltenberg I]] \n|-\n| align=center | [[File:Per-Kristian Foss 20090913-1.JPG|100x100px]]\n! scope=row | [[Per-Kristian Foss]]\n| style=\"background:#AACCFF\" | [[Conservative Party (Norway)|Conservative]] || {{dts|format=dmy|2001|10|19}} || {{dts|format=dmy|2005|10|17}} || {{ayd|2001|10|19|2005|10|17}} || [[Second cabinet Bondevik|Bondevik II]]\n|-\n| align=center | [[File:Norges finansminister Kristin Halvorsen vid Nordiska Radets session i Helsingfors 2008-10-28 (1).jpg|100x100px]]\n! scope=row | [[Kristin Halvorsen]]\n| style=\"background:#F4AAC2\" | [[Socialist Left Party (Norway)|Socialist Left]] || {{dts|format=dmy|2005|10|17}} || {{dts|format=dmy|2009|10|20}} || {{ayd|2005|10|17|2009|10|20}} || [[Second cabinet Stoltenberg|Stoltenberg II]] \n|-\n| align=center | [[File:Norges finansminister Sigbjoern Johnsen. Nordiskt finansministermote i Kopenhamn 2009-12-04.jpg|100x100px]]\n! scope=row | [[Sigbj\u00f8rn Johnsen]]\n| style=\"background:#FFB6B6\" | [[Labour Party (Norway)|Labour]] || {{dts|format=dmy|2009|10|20}} || {{dts|format=dmy|2013|10|16}} || {{ayd|2009|10|20|2013|10|16}} || [[Second cabinet Stoltenberg|Stoltenberg II]] \n|-\n| align=center | [[File:SivJensen2361 2E jpg DF0000062813.jpg|100x100px]]\n! scope=row | [[Siv Jensen]]\n| style=\"background:#E1AFF8\" | [[Progress Party (Norway)|Progress]] || {{dts|format=dmy|2013|10|16}} || {{dts|format=dmy|2020|1|24}}|| {{age in years and days|2013|10|16|2020|1|24}} || [[Solberg's Cabinet|Solberg]] \n|-\n| align=center | [[File:Jan Tore Sanner - 2010-05-08 at 10-34-24.jpg|100x100px]] \n! scope=row | [[Jan Tore Sanner]]\n| style=\