te=June 15, 2006 |url=https://www.thestar.com/NASApp/cs/ContentServer?pagename=thestar/Layout/Article_Type1&c=Article&cid=1150235412303&call_pageid=970599119419 |title=Pop & Rock |website=[[Toronto Star]] |accessdate=September 8, 2006 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060908220111/http://www.thestar.com/NASApp/cs/ContentServer?pagename=thestar%2FLayout%2FArticle_Type1&c=Article&cid=1150235412303&call_pageid=970599119419 |archivedate=September 8, 2006 |url-status=dead}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Incinerate\">{{Cite web |url=http://www.sonicyouth.com/mustang/lp/ep59.html |title=Incinerate |website=Sonicyouth.com |accessdate=May 7, 2016 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100811093934/http://sonicyouth.com/mustang/lp/ep59.html |archivedate=August 11, 2010 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Outtakes\">{{Cite web |url=http://www.sonicyouth.com/mustang/lp/ep57.html |title=Helen Lundeberg/Eyeliner |website=Sonicyouth.com |accessdate=May 7, 2016 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305222932/http://sonicyouth.com/mustang/lp/ep57.html |archivedate=March 5, 2016 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"CBGB performance\">{{Cite web |url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/58139/sonic-youth-celebrates-ripped-at-cbgb |title=Sonic Youth Celebrates 'Ripped' At CBGB |website=[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]] |date=June 14, 2006 |accessdate=May 7, 2016 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151121174525/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/58139/sonic-youth-celebrates-ripped-at-cbgb |archivedate=November 21, 2015 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Tour dates\">{{Cite web |url=http://www.brooklynvegan.com/sonic-youths-ra/ |title=Sonic Youth's Rather Ripped - Album Stream, Pitchfork vs The Voice, Tour Dates, etc... |website=[[BrooklynVegan]] |date=June 12, 2006 |accessdate=May 7, 2016 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160505212614/http://www.brooklynvegan.com/sonic-youths-ra/ |archivedate=May 5, 2016 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Music videos\">{{Cite web |url=http://www.filmcomment.com/article/eletrik-alchemy-claire-denis-films-sonic-youth |title=Eletrik Alchemy: Claire Denis Films Sonic Youth |website=[[Film Comment]] |date=January 2008 |author=Daniel Stuyck |accessdate=May 7, 2016 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150727021614/http://www.filmcomment.com/article/eletrik-alchemy-claire-denis-films-sonic-youth |archivedate=July 27, 2015 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Metacritic\">{{Cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/music/rather-ripped/sonic-youth |title=Rather Ripped |website=[[Metacritic]] |accessdate=May 8, 2016 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140728113349/http://www.metacritic.com/music/rather-ripped/sonic-youth |archivedate=July 28, 2014 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"NY Times\">{{Cite web |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2006/06/12/arts/music/12choi.html?pagewanted=all&_r=0 |title=Rather Ripped |website=[[The New York Times]] |date=June 12, 2006 |author=Ben Ratliff |authorlink=Ben Ratliff |accessdate=May 9, 2016 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160113053541/http://www.nytimes.com/2006/06/12/arts/music/12choi.html?pagewanted=all&_r=0 |archivedate=January 13, 2016 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"LA Times review\">{{Cite web |url=https://articles.latimes.com/2006/jun/11/entertainment/ca-rack11 |title=Love, pop the Sonic Youth way |website=[[Los Angeles Times]] |date=June 11, 2006 |author=Steve Hochman |accessdate=May 9, 2016 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160113053540/http://articles.latimes.com/2006/jun/11/entertainment/ca-rack11 |archivedate=January 13, 2016 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"EW review\">{{Cite web |url=https://www.ew.com/article/2006/06/12/rather-ripped |title=Rather Ripped |website=[[Entertainment Weekly]] |date=June 12, 2006 |author=Tom Sinclair |accessdate=May 10, 2016 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160113053540/http://www.ew.com/article/2006/06/12/rather-ripped |archivedate=January 13, 2016 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Pitchfork Top 2006\">{{Cite web |url=http://www.pitchforkmedia.com/article/feature/40007-staff-list-top-50-albums-of-2006 |title=Top 50 Albums of 2006 |website=[[Pitchfork (website)|Pitchfork]] |date=December 19, 2006 |accessdate=January 9, 2008 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080109003953/http://www.pitchforkmedia.com/article/feature/40007-staff-list-top-50-albums-of-2006 |archivedate=January 9, 2008 |url-status=dead}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"RS Top 2006\">{{Cite web |url=https://www.rollingstone.com/news/coverstory/50albums |title=The Top 50 Albums of the Year |website=[[Rolling Stone]] |date=December 29, 2006 |accessdate=June 19, 2008 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080619072538/http://www.rollingstone.com/news/coverstory/50albums |archivedate=June 19, 2008 |url-status=dead}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"AllMusic Review\">{{Cite web |url=https://www.allmusic.com/album/rather-ripped-mw0000775736 |title=Rather Ripped |website=[[AllMusic]] |author=Heather Phares |accessdate=May 4, 2016 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160131143744/http://www.allmusic.com/album/rather-ripped-mw0000775736 |archivedate=January 31, 2016 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"The Guardian Review\">{{Cite web |url=https://www.theguardian.com/music/2006/jun/02/popandrock.shopping9 |title=Sonic Youth, Rather Ripped |website=[[The Guardian]] |author=Dave Simpson |date=June 2, 2006 |accessdate=May 4, 2016 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160314041733/http://www.theguardian.com/music/2006/jun/02/popandrock.shopping9 |archivedate=March 14, 2016 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"RS Review\">{{Cite web |url=https://www.rollingstone.com/music/albumreviews/rather-ripped-20060612 |title=Rather Ripped |website=[[Rolling Stone]] |author=[[Rob Sheffield]] |date=June 12, 2006 |accessdate=May 4, 2016 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160113053541/http://www.rollingstone.com/music/albumreviews/rather-ripped-20060612 |archivedate=January 13, 2016 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"PopMatters Review\">{{Cite web |url=https://www.popmatters.com/review/sonic-youth-rather-ripped/ |title=Rather Ripped |website=[[PopMatters]] |author=Dave Heaton |date=June 9, 2006 |accessdate=May 4, 2016 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160308164027/http://www.popmatters.com/review/sonic-youth-rather-ripped/ |archivedate=March 8, 2016 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Slant Review\">{{Cite web |url=https://www.slantmagazine.com/music/review/sonic-youth-rather-ripped |title=Rather Ripped |website=[[Slant Magazine]] |author=Jimmy Newlin |date=June 12, 2006 |accessdate=May 4, 2016 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160113053540/http://www.slantmagazine.com/music/review/sonic-youth-rather-ripped |archivedate=January 13, 2016 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"CG\">{{Cite web |title=Sonic Youth: Rather Ripped |author=Robert Christgau |authorlink=Robert Christgau |date=2007 |url=https://www.robertchristgau.com/xg/cg/rhapsody-07.php |website=Robertchristgau.com |accessdate=February 4, 2017 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303222855/http://www.robertchristgau.com/xg/cg/rhapsody-07.php |archivedate=March 3, 2016 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Pitchfork review\">{{Cite web |url=https://pitchfork.com/reviews/albums/9059-rather-ripped/ |title=Rather Ripped |website=[[Pitchfork (website)|Pitchfork]] |author=Brandon Stosuy |date=June 12, 2006 |accessdate=February 25, 2016 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160113053539/http://pitchfork.com/reviews/albums/9059-rather-ripped/ |archivedate=January 13, 2016 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Charts Australia\">{{Cite web |url=http://australian-charts.com/showitem.asp?interpret=Sonic+Youth&titel=Rather+Ripped&cat=a |title=Australian albums charts \u2013 Sonic Youth \u2013 Rather Ripped |website=Australian-charts.com |accessdate=April 24, 2016 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160418081810/http://www.